Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者蕾貝卡  爆誕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拼命努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有七海把衣服穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  別在意
